23
00:01:09,420 --> 00:01:12,040
You do not need to worry about infrastructure provisioning,

24
00:01:12,050 --> 00:01:14,920
installing, and maintaining database software.

25
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:16,430
Highly scalable.

26
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:18,580
You can vertically scale your databases,

27
00:01:18,580 --> 00:01:20,640
